name: add-magnet-link
description: easyily add magnet links via a simple URL and your qBittorrent API endpoint

scripts.secret:local: node -e "process.stdout.write(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('base64'))" | wrangler secret put SECRET_KEY --config wrangler.local.toml
scripts.deploy:local: npm run secret:local && wrangler deploy --config wrangler.local.toml
